<paragraph id="4906C17BECE696E6EDBC3CADE602D1DD" pageId="0" pageNumber="339">K 1531, Thailand, Pai, on leaves and twigs of an undetermined dicotyledonous tree, 13.XI.2019, I.A. Gavrilov-Zimin.</paragraph>
